WEBVTT

00:00:04.714 --> 00:00:09.927
Is the destiny of mankind controlled
by some transcendental entity or Law?

00:00:10.803 --> 00:00:13.806
Is it like the hand of
God hovering above?

00:00:14.932 --> 00:00:16.600
At least it is true...

00:00:17.143 --> 00:00:20.646
...that man has no
control, even over his own will.

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:26.652
We are reaching a crucial moment.

00:00:27.028 --> 00:00:28.154
Our backs are to the river!

00:00:28.654 --> 00:00:29.530
There's no way to escape!

00:00:33.909 --> 00:00:35.327
Stake your lives on this fight!

00:00:35.578 --> 00:00:37.830
To survive, we have no choice
but to stake our lives on this fight!

00:00:38.664 --> 00:00:39.915
If we are able survive...

00:00:40.041 --> 00:00:41.333
...we are as good as victorious!

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:49.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:01:01.604 --> 00:01:03.689
<i>Feel no shame about shape.</i>

00:01:03.856 --> 00:01:05.649
<i>Weather changes the phrase.</i>

00:01:05.816 --> 00:01:09.320
<i>Even mother will
show you another way.</i>

00:01:09.570 --> 00:01:11.697
<i>So, put your glasses on.</i>

00:01:11.822 --> 00:01:13.824
<i>Nothing will be wrong.</i>

00:01:13.949 --> 00:01:16.035
<i>There's no blame, there's no fame.</i>

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:17.828
<i>It's up to you.</i>

00:01:18.079 --> 00:01:21.040
<i>The first words should be found.</i>

00:01:21.665 --> 00:01:25.086
<i>Whatever holds you back.</i>

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:26.462
<i>I...</i>

00:01:26.921 --> 00:01:27.588
<i>... can...</i>

00:01:27.713 --> 00:01:29.799
<i>I can get it off.</i>

00:01:29.965 --> 00:01:30.841
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:31.050 --> 00:01:31.801
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:31.967 --> 00:01:33.594
<i>Tell me what you want.</i>

00:01:33.844 --> 00:01:34.804
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:34.970 --> 00:01:35.721
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:35.846 --> 00:01:37.723
<i>I don't know why you are afraid.</i>

00:01:37.973 --> 00:01:38.849
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:39.058 --> 00:01:39.850
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:40.101 --> 00:01:41.477
<i>Tell me what you'd say.</i>

00:01:41.811 --> 00:01:42.812
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:43.062 --> 00:01:43.938
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:44.063 --> 00:01:44.730
<i>Too late...</i>

00:01:44.855 --> 00:01:46.315
<i>It's too late.</i>

00:01:51.612 --> 00:01:55.616
The Conqueror

00:02:29.900 --> 00:02:31.527
This dry sand is flying everywhere.

00:02:31.569 --> 00:02:32.695
I can't see anything.

00:02:33.154 --> 00:02:36.699
Well, it seems
certain that our army will win.

00:02:37.449 --> 00:02:40.953
Either way, everyone
guarding the castle has left.

00:02:41.453 --> 00:02:45.457
It's because they've been promised a
reward if they capture the enemy's head.

00:02:45.958 --> 00:02:48.460
They're just greedy,
every single one of them.

00:02:48.669 --> 00:02:51.463
Think of our rotten luck, here we are
standing as sentries at a time like this!

00:02:53.215 --> 00:02:54.466
Hey, what's wrong?

00:02:59.597 --> 00:03:00.347
The enemy?

00:03:00.806 --> 00:03:01.932
Where the hell did they come from?

00:03:09.231 --> 00:03:10.608
Charge!

00:03:16.113 --> 00:03:17.865
First formation,
block off the castle gates!

00:03:17.990 --> 00:03:20.326
Do not allow enemy
messengers to leave the castle!

00:03:20.451 --> 00:03:20.951
Got it!

00:03:21.118 --> 00:03:22.995
The rest of you,
carry out the operation!

00:03:23.495 --> 00:03:23.996
Hurry!

00:03:24.205 --> 00:03:25.581
There isn't a moment to lose!

00:03:31.629 --> 00:03:32.630
Is that...

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:38.969
You go from the right!

00:03:39.094 --> 00:03:39.511
Charge!

00:03:40.095 --> 00:03:41.889
Cover the castle
gate and the castle walls!

00:03:42.014 --> 00:03:43.766
Forget about their command center!

00:04:02.660 --> 00:04:04.286
Adon, to the rescue!

00:04:04.912 --> 00:04:06.121
It's you...

00:04:06.413 --> 00:04:08.415
I'll give you credit for
being a persistent devil.

00:04:11.043 --> 00:04:14.296
I am well known as the
indestructible baron, Adon!

00:04:14.672 --> 00:04:19.510
Everyone inevitably prostrates
themselves before my incredible vitality!

00:04:19.885 --> 00:04:23.889
I, Adon, already saw through
all your cheap tricks long ago!

00:04:24.390 --> 00:04:27.893
Therefore, I offered my
services as the castle guard...

00:04:28.018 --> 00:04:31.397
...and I waited patiently as you
marched ignorantly toward us.

00:04:31.772 --> 00:04:32.648
You lie.

00:04:32.773 --> 00:04:34.233
I do not lie!

00:04:34.608 --> 00:04:35.901
Everyone, step forward!

00:04:41.115 --> 00:04:42.116
Behold!

00:04:42.283 --> 00:04:44.868
The Blue Whale Super
Strong Heavy Assault Knights!

00:04:44.910 --> 00:04:48.163
I purposely left my troops inside
the castle for just such an occasion!

00:04:48.372 --> 00:04:52.167
Now, I am going to have my
revenge for the previous battle!

00:04:53.294 --> 00:04:54.253
Listen!

00:04:54.503 --> 00:04:57.506
Do not allow any of them
to escape with their lives.

00:04:57.798 --> 00:04:58.424
Charge!

00:05:00.926 --> 00:05:01.802
Let's go!

00:05:02.011 --> 00:05:04.054
I'll avenge my brother Samson's death!

00:05:04.179 --> 00:05:05.639
I give you no quarter!

00:05:28.162 --> 00:05:29.580
What's taking them?

00:05:29.788 --> 00:05:32.541
I have been kept waiting
for Griffith's capture too long!

00:05:32.708 --> 00:05:33.792
I have a report!

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:37.421
A single horseman of great skill
blocks our way to Count Griffith.

00:05:37.838 --> 00:05:40.341
Our armed force cannot
readily get closer to him...

00:05:40.591 --> 00:05:42.676
You are all helpless!

00:05:51.226 --> 00:05:52.603
What is he?

00:05:52.853 --> 00:05:54.605
Is there anyone who can stop him?

00:06:02.112 --> 00:06:03.739
General Boscogn!

00:06:03.947 --> 00:06:05.366
The General will do it...

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:42.486
What?

00:06:43.904 --> 00:06:44.863
Unbelievable...

00:06:45.030 --> 00:06:45.864
Stay out of it!

00:06:46.031 --> 00:06:47.741
We'll be in trouble if we get
caught up in that fierce battle!

00:06:57.418 --> 00:06:58.127
Amazing!

00:06:58.252 --> 00:06:59.753
That's our big sister all right!

00:07:00.921 --> 00:07:01.922
Why is it?

00:07:02.047 --> 00:07:04.550
Your swordplay is
so different than before!

00:07:04.925 --> 00:07:07.261
I wasn't feeling too well back then.

00:07:07.678 --> 00:07:09.555
The hell you weren't!

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.265
Don't make poor excuses...

00:07:12.433 --> 00:07:14.560
Wait until I'm finished speaking!

00:07:15.519 --> 00:07:17.688
Why don't you keep your
mouth closed for a moment?

00:07:20.774 --> 00:07:22.067
The enemy has only a small number!

00:07:22.192 --> 00:07:23.318
Don't let up, overcome them!

00:07:23.819 --> 00:07:27.281
The future of the
Hawks rests on this battle!

00:07:43.714 --> 00:07:45.215
Thank you, Pippin!

00:07:47.551 --> 00:07:48.844
Dammit!

00:07:48.969 --> 00:07:51.346
It's just a matter of time
before we're wiped out!

00:07:51.472 --> 00:07:53.098
Just look at their numbers!

00:07:53.599 --> 00:07:55.225
What are you talking about, Corkus?

00:07:55.434 --> 00:07:56.560
Are you saying we should desert?

00:07:58.228 --> 00:07:59.813
I'm not saying that, but...

00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:04.735
If I have to desert to live,
I might as well die in this battle!

00:08:05.444 --> 00:08:06.236
Oh, no!

00:08:06.361 --> 00:08:08.113
Little Ricket has gone insane!

00:08:09.990 --> 00:08:10.574
He's right!

00:08:11.366 --> 00:08:12.951
I agree with Ricket!

00:08:16.371 --> 00:08:19.124
My army is utterly overwhelming them!

00:08:19.708 --> 00:08:20.501
Attack them!

00:08:20.709 --> 00:08:22.628
Keep on attacking
and overpower them!

00:08:24.004 --> 00:08:30.093
Boscogn, why are you spending so
much time in battle with a mere horseman?

00:08:36.808 --> 00:08:37.768
Strong!

00:08:38.519 --> 00:08:39.645
This guy is...

00:08:39.811 --> 00:08:40.938
...truly strong...

00:08:42.064 --> 00:08:46.276
My death feels closer now than
when I was slaughtering a hundred men.

00:08:47.027 --> 00:08:49.571
I'm going to have to put
everything on the line now...

00:08:50.072 --> 00:08:51.031
...or I'll die!

00:08:55.577 --> 00:08:56.537
No...

00:08:57.704 --> 00:08:59.331
I've been through worse...

00:09:07.589 --> 00:09:10.676
This hopelessness is nothing
compared to what I felt then...

00:09:34.992 --> 00:09:36.618
How dare you...

00:09:36.827 --> 00:09:38.620
Only one thing to do now!

00:09:42.207 --> 00:09:43.500
I am terribly sorry!

00:09:44.209 --> 00:09:44.751
What?

00:09:45.335 --> 00:09:47.879
I beg your pardon for my lack
of courtesy, please forgive me!

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:52.259
After all, I'm just a lowly commander,
following orders from the General.

00:09:52.509 --> 00:09:55.345
Personally, I've never wanted
any sort of grudge against you!

00:09:55.887 --> 00:09:56.388
Now, now...

00:09:56.513 --> 00:09:58.473
Please take this castle if you wish!

00:09:59.016 --> 00:10:01.018
I'm the last person who
would stand in your way...

00:10:01.143 --> 00:10:03.520
...and I would like to
thank you for sparing my life!

00:10:05.022 --> 00:10:06.648
You are a disgusting man...

00:10:08.358 --> 00:10:10.652
My clever ruse has put you off guard...

00:10:15.032 --> 00:10:15.741
Big Sister!

00:10:16.783 --> 00:10:18.619
Foolish woman!

00:10:19.286 --> 00:10:23.415
That was <i>Ressha Jinrai,</i> the
secret art of the crossbow sneak attack...

00:10:23.540 --> 00:10:25.876
...passed down through the
Coborlwitz family for one thousand years!

00:10:26.418 --> 00:10:29.630
The tip of the arrow was poisoned,
and it will numb your entire body.

00:10:30.631 --> 00:10:34.801
Your days of sinful
deeds are over, you evil bitch!

00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:36.511
I can't afford...

00:10:36.803 --> 00:10:39.431
...to waste my time
playing your foolish games...

00:10:41.933 --> 00:10:42.517
...any longer!

00:10:56.573 --> 00:10:57.824
It's ruined!

00:10:58.075 --> 00:11:00.702
My sword was chipped and cracked
during the fight against a hundred men...

00:11:05.582 --> 00:11:06.708
This is the end...

00:11:07.084 --> 00:11:08.460
...for the Commander of the Raiders!

00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:21.473
Here I come!

00:11:23.350 --> 00:11:25.102
I might be able to keep you alive...

00:11:25.310 --> 00:11:29.106
...as my personal toy,
if you obediently give up now.

00:11:30.232 --> 00:11:31.983
But, if you refuse...

00:11:34.319 --> 00:11:38.240
Take that, and that!

00:11:39.741 --> 00:11:42.828
Take that and that and that!

00:11:44.246 --> 00:11:46.873
Dammit, my body is
numb and I'm helpless...

00:11:47.457 --> 00:11:48.500
Big Sister!

00:12:00.887 --> 00:12:02.764
Well, what are you going to do?

00:12:02.889 --> 00:12:04.391
You can no longer evade my blows...

00:12:08.645 --> 00:12:10.605
I'll get you back for
what you did to my face!

00:12:10.772 --> 00:12:13.358
First I'll chop off
your arms and your legs!

00:12:13.775 --> 00:12:17.779
Then you can explain whether
or not you want to be my captive...

00:12:17.988 --> 00:12:20.031
...and I'll listen at my leisure!

00:12:20.782 --> 00:12:22.409
Your legs go first!

00:12:25.996 --> 00:12:26.538
What?

00:12:33.503 --> 00:12:34.171
Impossible!

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.927
You were a fairly interesting man.

00:12:41.303 --> 00:12:43.805
As well as an
irredeemable, revolting bastard!

00:12:52.939 --> 00:12:53.523
Now!

00:12:53.648 --> 00:12:54.775
The rest are no match for us!

00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:55.817
Cut them down!

00:13:06.828 --> 00:13:07.579
Now then...

00:13:18.089 --> 00:13:19.591
Help the Commander!

00:13:20.175 --> 00:13:20.842
Get back!

00:13:21.092 --> 00:13:22.052
You're no match for him!

00:13:22.427 --> 00:13:23.804
Unwanted fools!

00:13:45.116 --> 00:13:45.742
Guts!

00:13:45.867 --> 00:13:46.743
Take up that sword!

00:14:15.272 --> 00:14:17.482
He did it, finally!

00:14:17.732 --> 00:14:18.650
Amazing...

00:14:21.111 --> 00:14:22.863
He's utterly helpless...

00:14:23.280 --> 00:14:24.239
That can't be!

00:14:24.281 --> 00:14:26.408
Sir Boscogn is an invincible knight...

00:14:26.533 --> 00:14:28.034
Don't be a fool!

00:14:28.243 --> 00:14:29.661
Even without the General...

00:14:29.786 --> 00:14:31.538
...nothing can effect
our army's advantage!

00:14:31.663 --> 00:14:32.539
We can't let up now!

00:14:33.915 --> 00:14:35.500
Governor, look at that!

00:14:35.876 --> 00:14:36.668
What's that?

00:14:49.180 --> 00:14:50.807
T-That is...

00:14:51.308 --> 00:14:52.434
The enemy's flag?

00:14:52.684 --> 00:14:54.185
Our castle surrendered?

00:14:54.311 --> 00:14:55.562
What's the meaning of this?

00:14:55.937 --> 00:14:58.189
Don't you get it yet?

00:14:58.773 --> 00:15:00.400
Your head has been cut off!

00:15:00.525 --> 00:15:01.401
Your castle has fallen!

00:15:01.943 --> 00:15:03.570
Don't tell me you
haven't figured it out yet?

00:15:03.778 --> 00:15:05.697
You've been completely defeated!

00:15:06.031 --> 00:15:07.324
We lost?

00:15:07.949 --> 00:15:08.825
Did we?

00:15:10.702 --> 00:15:12.037
Everyone, shout!

00:15:12.203 --> 00:15:13.330
Give a shout of triumph!

00:15:26.843 --> 00:15:29.429
From now on, we will hunt
the remnants of the enemy.

00:15:30.096 --> 00:15:32.223
Only let the enemy pass
if they immediately flee!

00:15:32.349 --> 00:15:35.101
If they resist,
exterminate every last one them!

00:15:45.487 --> 00:15:46.738
Wait, everyone!

00:15:46.988 --> 00:15:48.365
I am the commander-in-chief!

00:15:48.865 --> 00:15:50.241
I am still alive!

00:16:13.890 --> 00:16:14.891
Griffith...

00:16:15.517 --> 00:16:17.769
It's been a while, Governor Gennon...

00:16:19.521 --> 00:16:21.272
Oh, Griffith...

00:16:22.983 --> 00:16:24.526
I missed you so much.

00:16:24.651 --> 00:16:26.403
You and I always helped one another.

00:16:26.528 --> 00:16:28.530
So, you are going to let me
escape unharmed, aren't you?

00:16:30.740 --> 00:16:33.284
I even gave my soldiers the order that...

00:16:33.660 --> 00:16:36.121
...you were not to be
harmed under any circumstance.

00:16:36.663 --> 00:16:39.541
You understand the feelings
within my heart, don't you?

00:16:40.291 --> 00:16:43.253
Not a day passed
that I did not think of you.

00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:46.631
We loved each other
passionately on that night...

00:16:47.298 --> 00:16:50.051
You will listen to my plea, won't you?

00:16:54.305 --> 00:16:55.306
You don't...

00:16:56.391 --> 00:16:58.685
...bear any ill will toward me, do you?

00:16:59.394 --> 00:17:01.813
I do not bear any ill
feelings at all, Governor.

00:17:02.439 --> 00:17:03.940
Oh, then you...

00:17:04.441 --> 00:17:08.028
However, it upsets me when
you speak of us making love...

00:17:08.528 --> 00:17:13.366
...for I feel absolutely
nothing for you at all.

00:17:13.616 --> 00:17:15.243
Neither ill feelings or otherwise...

00:17:15.368 --> 00:17:17.287
What are you talking about, Griffith?

00:17:17.912 --> 00:17:23.043
I took advantage of an opportunity
and you happened to be there at the time.

00:17:23.918 --> 00:17:25.920
I just picked up a
pebble lying in my path...

00:17:26.046 --> 00:17:29.174
...and it happened to
be none other than you.

00:17:31.176 --> 00:17:32.052
Y-You bastard!

00:17:36.181 --> 00:17:40.810
At any rate, a chattering
pebble can be quite a nuisance.

00:17:50.945 --> 00:17:51.446
Unbelievable!

00:17:51.571 --> 00:17:53.073
We finally made it!

00:17:53.156 --> 00:17:54.783
Can you believe it?

00:17:56.201 --> 00:17:57.202
Are you all right?

00:17:57.410 --> 00:17:58.078
Yeah...

00:17:58.203 --> 00:17:59.954
I'm feeling a bit better...

00:18:00.580 --> 00:18:02.165
Don't worry about me.

00:18:02.290 --> 00:18:05.585
You must go check to see if
any enemies remain within the castle.

00:18:05.710 --> 00:18:06.336
Yes!

00:18:06.711 --> 00:18:07.337
Hey, get moving.

00:18:07.462 --> 00:18:08.338
We've got a job to do!

00:18:08.463 --> 00:18:09.172
All right!

00:18:37.367 --> 00:18:39.077
Hey, good job.

00:18:40.954 --> 00:18:42.205
What's wrong?

00:18:42.705 --> 00:18:44.499
Just a scratch...

00:18:45.834 --> 00:18:48.086
But to tell you the truth...

00:18:48.753 --> 00:18:50.505
I want you to give me your shoulder.

00:19:00.515 --> 00:19:01.891
Amazing...

00:19:04.644 --> 00:19:05.603
Hey...

00:19:05.728 --> 00:19:07.147
I always feel like this...

00:19:08.648 --> 00:19:12.110
Whenever I see Griffith
surrounded by his comrades like that...

00:19:13.278 --> 00:19:15.613
I don't know why, but my
heart becomes filled with sorrow.

00:19:16.114 --> 00:19:18.408
Because he seems to be so far away...

00:19:19.909 --> 00:19:21.161
...beyond my reach.

00:19:28.501 --> 00:19:30.044
That's not true...

00:19:33.423 --> 00:19:34.883
Hey, what are you doing!

00:19:35.508 --> 00:19:36.426
Let's go.

00:19:38.178 --> 00:19:40.555
To see your captain.

00:19:44.767 --> 00:19:45.643
Yeah...

00:19:56.696 --> 00:19:57.947
No, it couldn't have been...

00:20:12.837 --> 00:20:15.423
The time of the great Eclipse is near.

00:20:15.798 --> 00:20:18.218
And the devils will soon descend...

00:20:30.438 --> 00:20:32.357
The Castle of Doldrey fell.

00:20:32.482 --> 00:20:35.610
For the time being,
our long war will be over.

00:20:35.860 --> 00:20:37.487
Then, Griffith will be free...

00:20:37.570 --> 00:20:42.325
...to let his political views intrude
into the administration our kingdom.

00:20:42.617 --> 00:20:46.371
He is shameless enough to do
such things despite his low social rank.

00:20:46.704 --> 00:20:50.083
His Majesty seems to
rely upon him very much.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:55.380
Because of his services rendered,
he will attain the position of General.

00:20:55.588 --> 00:20:56.381
Really?

00:20:56.631 --> 00:20:59.509
His Majesty will give
the Hawks the title of White Knights...

00:20:59.634 --> 00:21:02.637
...only born by the White Tigers and
the White Dragon Knights until now.

00:21:02.762 --> 00:21:05.390
That title indicates supreme
command of our entire army!

00:21:05.598 --> 00:21:06.516
Nonsense!

00:21:06.766 --> 00:21:08.977
Now he'll be even more inflated!

00:21:09.602 --> 00:21:15.400
However, it has been proven that his
survival skills are lacking within the castle...

00:21:16.150 --> 00:21:17.151
What is that?

00:21:17.610 --> 00:21:18.778
Antiaris...

00:21:18.987 --> 00:21:20.405
...a poison that acts instantaneously...

00:21:20.530 --> 00:21:22.156
We shall use this on him...

00:21:22.782 --> 00:21:24.867
Are you sure about this?

00:21:25.034 --> 00:21:27.870
No matter what, our scheme
must not be traced back to us.

00:21:27.996 --> 00:21:31.291
We will not do such a thing personally.

00:21:31.666 --> 00:21:32.542
However...

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:34.043
Do not fear.

00:21:38.923 --> 00:21:40.258
Your Majesty!

00:21:40.925 --> 00:21:44.053
You can leave everything in my hands...

00:22:03.156 --> 00:22:05.283
<i>Looking back, the morning comes.</i>

00:22:05.408 --> 00:22:08.911
<i>Don't find your face in your glass.</i>

00:22:10.163 --> 00:22:12.957
<i>Take the moonlight by the tail.</i>

00:22:13.082 --> 00:22:15.960
<i>It's a rainy sight that you're shading.</i>

00:22:17.670 --> 00:22:19.172
<i>What is that?</i>

00:22:19.297 --> 00:22:20.465
<i>It's just the same.</i>

00:22:20.590 --> 00:22:23.593
<i>What is trying on your crown?</i>

00:22:24.927 --> 00:22:27.805
<i>I'm spending my
glass and walking back.</i>

00:22:27.930 --> 00:22:31.100
<i>So wear my glass, you're fading.</i>

00:22:31.476 --> 00:22:34.729
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:35.188 --> 00:22:38.107
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:38.816 --> 00:22:41.861
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:42.737 --> 00:22:45.490
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:46.449 --> 00:22:49.327
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:50.244 --> 00:22:51.996
<i>I'm waiting...</i>

